set_zoom

set_zoom.Rd

set_zoom applies a zoom to the depiction

set_zoom(dg, zoom = 1)

Arguments

dg

Required. A Depiction Generator probably created by depiction#' @importFrom rJava .jcall
zoom

Optional. Default 1

Examples

pen    <- parse_smiles("CC1(C(N2C(S1)C(C2=O)NC(=O)CC3=CC=CC=C3)C(=O)[O-])C penicillin")
depiction() %>%
  set_zoom(3) %>%
  depict(pen) %>%
  get_image()
